&lt;a href=&#34;/publication/32698440&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;32698440&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:center;&#34;&gt;
The results indicated that the SARS-CoV-2 infection strongly activates TNF and NFκB-signaling pathways through significant upregulation of the TNF, IL1B, IL6, IL8, NFKB1, NFKB2 and RELB genes.
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
